COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
State of Oklahoma
SPEAKER:
CHAIR:
I move to amend amendment HB3581 POLPCS1
Of the printed Bill
Page 3 Section 1 Lines 14-15
Of the Engrossed Bill
By deleting all language beginning with the word "owned" on Line 14
through the word "authority" on Line 15; and
Page 14, Section 4, Line 3: By deleting the "November 1, 2026" effective
date and inserting in lieu thereof, the following:
"It being immediately necessary for the preservation of the public peace,
health or safety, an emergency is hereby declared to exist, by reason
whereof this act shall take effect and be in full force from and after its
passage and approval."
